{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1631372513.1135545", "card_id": "Q_485405656", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 739}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你都知道哪些诈骗分子的常用「套路」？怎么才能一眼识破那些很唬人诈骗手法？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "警官老陈直播宣传反诈「出圈」，最近反诈宣传力度这么大，你知道哪些常用的「套路」？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-5d11eb510ea673ab087e4c5f4632b6fe_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2297 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485405656"}}, "attached_info": "ClUImej34ZyFkvsVEAMaCDcwMTQ5ODY0IPWH3okGMEA4nxdAAHIJNDg1NDA1NjU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1631372513.1142561", "card_id": "Q_485281565", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 985}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果选一首最美的古诗词教孩子，你会选哪首，为什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近在和上小学的女儿一起背古诗，背到和秋天有关的诗词，她特别喜欢「山明水净夜来霜，数树深红出浅黄」这一句，觉得秋天很美，诗也很美。 然后问我能不能教她一首最美的诗？这确实不太好选择，如果选一首最美的古诗词，你会选哪首？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9b0b0edde89a5f31ce52279633cfa64f.jpg?source=2044ae36"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1717 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485281565"}}, "attached_info": "ClUImej34ZyFkvsVEAMaCDcwMTIyMjUwIOaQ3IkGMEI41BlAAXIJNDg1MjgxNTY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1631372513.1147528", "card_id": "Q_456957044", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 393}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "青春年华，你做过什么热血澎湃、值得骄傲的事情？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "无奋斗，不青春。在最美的青春年华，有人为革命事业慷慨献出生命，有人穿上军装保家卫国，有人用终身奋斗践行青春之诺。你的青春是什么模样？你做过最青春热血、值得铭记的事是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4f40da0f27231cf6333cacb52265d0ff_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1447 万热度"}, "label_area": {